  "name": "Glacial Blade",
  "ownership": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You brandish the weapon used in the spell's casting and make a melee attack with it against one creature within the weapon's reach. On a hit, the target suffers the weapon attack's normal effects, and it becomes encased in a thin sheet of frost until the start of your next turn. If the target uses its action to make a weapon attack, it immediately takes <strong>1d4 cold damage</strong>, and the spell ends.</p><p>This spell's damage increases when you reach certain levels. At 5th level, the damage the target takes for attacking increases to 2d4. The damage roll increases by 1d6 at 11th level (3d4) and again at 17th level (4d4).</p>",
